---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Nieuserver.online | Game Server Hub</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }
        
        body {
            background-color: #2a2a2a;
            color: #e0e0e0;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }
        
        header {
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7)), 
                        url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1550751827-4bd374c3f58b?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1350&q=80');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            height: 300px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            padding: 0 20px;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #4CAF50;
        }
        
        header h1 {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .card {
            background: #383838;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            border-left: 3px solid #4CAF50;
        }
        
        .card h2 {
            color: #4CAF50;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }
        
        .card p {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #b0b0b0;
        }
        
        footer {
            background: #1a1a1a;
            color: #e0e0e0;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 25px 0;
            margin-top: 50px;
            border-top: 2px solid #4CAF50;
        }
        
        nav {
            background: #1a1a1a;
            padding: 12px 0;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #4CAF50;
        }
        
        nav ul {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            list-style: none;
            gap: 15px;
        }
        
        nav ul li a {
            color: #e0e0e0;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 5px 10px;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        
        nav ul li a:hover {
            color: #4CAF50;
        }
        
        .active {
            color: #4CAF50;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .features {
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        
        .features li {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            margin-left: 20px;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            header {
                height: 250px;
            }
            
            header h1 {
                font-size: 1.8rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="/minecraft">Minecraft</a></li>
            <li><a href="/terraria">Terraria</a></li>
            <li><a href="/about" class="active">About</a></li>
            <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>
    
    <header>
        <h1>About Nieuserver.online</h1>
        <p>A straightforward hub for game server information</p>
    </header>
    
    <div class="container">
        <div class="card">
            <h2>What This Is</h2>
            <p>Nieuserver.online is a website that provides information about our Minecraft and Terraria game servers. It's designed to be a simple, functional resource for players who want to connect to our servers or check their status.</p>
            <p>We're not claiming to be the biggest or most advanced server network - just a place where friends and like-minded players can enjoy these games together.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card">
            <h2>What We Actually Offer</h2>
            <ul class="features">
                <li>Basic server status information (online/offline, player count)</li>
                <li>Connection details for each server</li>
                <li>Simple rules and guidelines</li>
                <li>Occasional announcements about maintenance or updates</li>
                <li>A contact form for support questions</li>
            </ul>
            <p>The website is hosted on a standard shared hosting plan, which keeps costs low but means we have typical limitations on traffic and performance.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card">
            <h2>Technical Details</h2>
            <p>For those interested in the technical side:</p>
            <ul class="features">
                <li>Static HTML/CSS website (no fancy frameworks)</li>
                <li>Basic server status checks via PHP scripts</li>
                <li>Mobile-responsive design (works okay on phones)</li>
                <li>No user accounts or complex features</li>
            </ul>
            <p>We prioritize reliability over cutting-edge features. The site does what it needs to do without unnecessary complexity.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card">
            <h2>About the Servers</h2>
            <p>Our game servers run on:</p>
            <ul class="features">
                <li>Minecraft: PaperMC with basic plugins</li>
                <li>Terraria: TShock with standard configuration</li>
            </ul>
            <p>They're hosted on a mid-range VPS that can handle 20-30 concurrent players comfortably. We don't claim 100% uptime, but we do our best to keep them running smoothly.</p>
            <p>These are community servers, not professional hosting services. We welcome players who want a casual, friendly experience.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2025 nieuserver.online</p>
        <p>A simple service for game server information</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>